{"tid":13813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕人上車機會黎啦！！！！","createTime":"2016-11-30T08:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T00:26:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c55a7e62700ebabb31430b995b424a37cf7e523","tid":13813,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"　《經濟通通訊社３０日專訊》俊和發展集團（母公司為亞洲聯合基建（００７１１））聯席<br />\n主席彭一庭於記者會表示，集團位於屯門新盤命名為「青雋」，集團預計最快下月可以獲得預售<br />\n樓花同意書，當獲得同意書後便會部署推售。<br />\n　　項目涉及３５６伙，由開放式至兩房單位不等，實用面積介乎１２８至７６３平方呎，集團<br />\n不評論項目未來售價參考目標。<br />\n　　但俊和地產發展董事潘志才強調，單位設計將符合年青人需求，例如希望擁有私人空間及較<br />\n少在家煮食家庭，故大部分單位，包括開放式及一房均採用開放式廚房設計。<br />\n　　彭氏補充，由於首次置業需求仍然旺盛，雖然政府「加辣」，但認為措施只針對投資需求，<br />\n故預計樓市未來仍會平穩發展，集團亦不會刻意以高價搶地。"},{"pid":"35147377ad713b0f504081762e958d751d708b00","tid":13813,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"蓋清你住邊區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f327ffff2027434a2924150e79a0b83686088860","tid":13813,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"128呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d894b22dbd8bef42a99a601ec6b7cb01b7de13","tid":13813,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>128呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保安個位都大過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f4ef5eb506a709e8e88510b6a4e9c761b655b6","tid":13813,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"128 呎 , 賣 300 萬  是常識吧 ?"},{"pid":"c465b53fd819472145b115c4401ed4414e2c56d3","tid":13813,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>128 呎 , 賣 300 萬  是常識吧 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屯門兩萬蚊尺！大小唔緊要！ 最緊要400 萬以下！同外母講有樓！！"},{"pid":"3a503f6837230cc1a0716cd10b5e2068fe2ca388","tid":13813,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>128呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保安個位都大過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n128呎入面有20呎係環保露台😍"},{"pid":"9592b590a2f1583b45a79f3e00fb1c42e07200a3","tid":13813,"uid":33622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:54:38.000Z","msg":"【終極劏房】全港最細128呎！ 俊和：參考學生宿舍 「皇帝都係睏張床」<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55985724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55985724&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=882020ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55985724&h=15d36863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55985724</a><br />\n<br />\n俊和董事潘志才指，項目設計參考學生宿舍，「睇到學生宿舍好感動，未聽過有家長投訴學生宿舍坎坷。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘志才更形容好多年輕人食完飯就返房，甚少下廚煮食，鐘意響自已個房，所以好多年輕人需要既係一個房，就算皇帝擁有紫禁城，都只係睏張床。他認為重要的是「有限空間、活出無限」、「有Enjoyable嘅空間」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味"},{"pid":"2184171feb9b9ad7bb15406c4228435275ebea89","tid":13813,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"其實俾三球野買新樓百幾呎，<br />\n做咩唔買舊樓唐樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見旺角油麻地都係一萬蚊呎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2969851ffe01b6a27b934b01575fb37434abcdf","tid":13813,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【終極劏房】全港最細128呎！ 俊和：參考學生宿舍 「皇帝都係睏張床」<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;amp;s=7015342&amp;amp;a=55985724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26amp%3Bs%3D7015342%26amp%3Ba%3D55985724&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5872e3bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26amp%3Bs%3D7015342%26amp%3Ba%3D55985724&h=6481b822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;amp;s=7015342&amp;amp;a=55985724</a><br />\n<br />\n俊和董事潘志才指，項目設計參考學生宿舍，「睇到學生宿舍好感動，未聽過有家長投訴學生宿舍坎坷。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘志才更形容好多年輕人食完飯就返房，甚少下廚煮食，鐘意響自已個房，所以好多年輕人需要既係一個房，就算皇帝擁有紫禁城，都只係睏張床。他認為重要的是「有限空間、活出無限」、「有Enjoyable嘅空間」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依 D 人死全家都唔撚夠 ,  咁撚樣講野都得 <br />\n咁佢全家訓棺材其實都同訓床差唔多啫"},{"pid":"c1158bb160c83c47702395a29bb5e262e81206fa","tid":13813,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實俾三球野買新樓百幾呎，<br />\n做咩唔買舊樓唐樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見旺角油麻地都係一萬蚊呎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太舊成萬蚊呎你又會覺得唔值架喎<br />\n同埋, 太舊要揹個維